Style instruction:
{% if style == "poetic" -%}
Turn this memory into a poetic visual. Focus on symbolism, quiet emotion, soft natural light, and small meaningful objects. Make it feel like a personal memory, not a fantasy poster.
{% elif style == "cinematic" -%}
Make this look like a cinematic still from a personal film. Use realistic lighting, emotional framing, natural depth of field, subtle color grading, and an intimate story-driven composition. Avoid making it look like a movie poster.
{% elif style == "minimalist" -%}
Create a minimalist visual with lots of negative space, a restrained color palette, clean composition, and one strong emotional symbol from the memory. Keep it calm, simple, and premium.
{% elif style == "dreamy" -%}
Reimagine this memory as a dreamlike scene. Use soft atmosphere, gentle surreal details, blurred emotional boundaries, glowing light, and expressive color while staying connected to the real memory.
{% elif style == "illustrated" -%}
Turn this into a warm editorial illustration. Use expressive hand-drawn details, natural proportions, rich but controlled color, and a modern storybook-like composition.
{% elif style == "watercolor" -%}
Transform this memory into a delicate watercolor image. Use soft paper texture, translucent pigment, gentle color bleeding, muted tones, and imperfect hand-painted edges.
{% endif %}

Intensity instruction:
{% if intensity == "subtle" -%}
Keep the transformation subtle and close to the original feeling. Avoid extreme changes.
{% elif intensity == "balanced" -%}
Balance realism and artistic interpretation. Make the mood clear without overdoing it.
{% elif intensity == "expressive" -%}
Push the emotion more strongly with bolder lighting, color, atmosphere, and symbolism while keeping the memory recognizable.
{% endif %}

